    <digest>
        Convert an image to a duotone
    </digest>

    <description>
        Convert an image to a duotone. Provide the two colors through inlets and set the curve for the grayscale image to affect the color range. Based on Micron's Duotone patch: https://www.patreon.com/posts/easy-duotone-19824702
    </description>
    
